{"id":383913,"date":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":22}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"96","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我家办起小鞍钢","ftitle":"","authors":["张波"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山东益都织布厂工人　张波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓风机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哼哼响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家办起“炼铁厂”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈当“技师”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶任“厂长”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐姐嫂嫂摇风箱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇的炉火伸舌头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼出铁水闪红光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别看我们工厂小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是祖国“小鞍钢”。"}]}